{"id":4175,"content":"<P class=MsoPlainText style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\">\r\n<P class=MsoPlainText style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><FONT face=宋体><SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><o:p><FONT face=宋体></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\"><STRONG>　　（三）曹雪芹逝世二百周年纪念活动<BR></STRONG><BR></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　在</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">运动</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">不断、治国手法一张一弛的</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">27</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年马鞍形演变中，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1961-1965</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年是对三年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">大跃进</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">天灾人祸的</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">调整、恢复</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">时期。副总理兼外交部长、直性汉子陈毅在该年有两篇诚恳、体贴、抚慰知识分子的讲话，一次发表于北京应届毕业大学生的集会中，另一次发表于在广州召开的文艺工作者座谈会上。这两篇讲话的广泛传达，使得</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">批胡</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">、</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">肃反</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">、</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">反右</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">形成的肃杀气氛和紧张的物资供应有所缓和。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1962</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">9</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月间在中共八届十中全会上，毛泽东</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">千万不要忘记阶级和阶级斗争</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">提法并未获得高层人士的普遍认同。以周恩来为例，他仍然致力于制造宽松、祥和的文化态势。据刘梦溪</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">红学三十年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">、韩进廉</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">红学史稿</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1963</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年大陆搞的曹雪芹逝世二百周年纪念，是遵照周恩来指示办的。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　因中央清除</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">资产阶级政治法律体系</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">而被投闲置散的英法学博士、原任北京大学教授，后任</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1952</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年合倂北大、清华、燕京有关学系组成的</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">北京政法学院</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">教授<?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags\" /><st1:PersonName w:st=\"on\" ProductID=\"吴恩裕\">吴恩裕</st1:PersonName>先生，在无课可开、</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">白吃人民小米</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">的情况下，不甘心四十多岁就光阴虚掷，苦闷之馀，转而研究《红楼梦》，十年间成绩斐然。据<st1:PersonName w:st=\"on\" ProductID=\"吴\">吴</st1:PersonName>先生</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">曹雪芹卒年考辨存稿·小引</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">陈述，由于原国民党总理哲嗣孙科太子系红人、大陆</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">中国国民党革命委员会</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">副主席王昆仑向周恩来推荐，吴恩裕负责了</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1963</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年北京</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">光明日报·文学遗产</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">发轫、以曹雪芹卒年的讨论带动全面的《红楼梦》热。吴恩裕说，那次讨论的开篇，是王昆仑在春间一再让他写，文学研究所所长何其芳也要他写、</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">光明日报</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">又来要文章，他就写了。引来的半年讨论，效果并不好。费力各报许多篇幅，不但对卒年未得出一致的结论，即对可据的基本材料，参加讨论双方的看法，也始终不能一致。到了</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">7</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月初，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">文学遗产</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">编者陈翔鹤打电话问吴有无必要继续讨论下去。吴恩裕说：结束了吧，再讨论下去看来也不会有什么结果。于是，又由吴写出结束讨论的文章。据此可见周恩来用吴恩裕这个党外人士来带头的作用。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　纪念曹雪芹逝世</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">200</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">周年的活动，还有重新出版《红楼梦》、舞台演出和电影拍摄《红楼梦》故事、刊登纪念和讨论文章、举办展览会、调查曹雪芹故居和墓地、探索、绘制和模拟大观园等等。其中盛举要数内容丰富，轰动一时的展览会。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　展览会在北京故宫文华殿举行，由中央文化部、文学艺术界联合会、作家协会、故宫博物院联合主办，展览分六个部分。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　第一部分是曹雪芹的生平和家世。展出曹氏宗谱、皇宗诰命、曹家奏折、抄家谕旨、家产清单、曹寅</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">楝亭诗抄</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">、关于曹雪芹的清人著作、以及当代名家的曹雪芹生平事迹绘画等。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　第而部分是《红楼梦》的时代背景。展出当年的地租、抗租、饥馑、当票、高利贷、卖儿、民反、纺织业、盐业、外贸、罢工、贵族餐具、贪官赃单、宫规、宫女自杀档案、束缚女性教材、恋情作品、婚姻、禁书令、科学、文字狱等所有《红楼梦》涉及，或有助于运用马列毛教条代绘画。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　第三部分是关于《红楼梦》的各种版本及其面世后的反响。展出众多抄本、刻本、外交译本；续书的研究、考证和评论；有关《红楼梦》的诗词歌赋戏曲等等。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　第四部分是《红楼梦》时代的参考对象。展出康熙、雍正、乾隆年间的日常用品、服装首饰以及园林建筑方面的实物和图画。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　第五部分和第六部分展出以《红楼梦》故事为题材的文学艺术作品――戏剧、电影、曲艺、绘画、雕塑，以及琳琅满目的工艺美术产品。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　荡漾着诗情画意、文采风流的升平景象，很快就被</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">斗天、斗地、斗人，其乐无穷</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">的毛</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">伏笔现形</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">所粉碎。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><STRONG><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　（四）</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">红学</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">的阶级观与园地的荒芜</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></STRONG></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　虽然</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">文革：爆发于</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1966</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">6</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月，实际上，毛泽东在</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1962</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">9</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月中共中央全会上强调</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">阶级和阶级斗争</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">后即开始部署。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1964</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">、</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1965</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年间，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">红学</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">领域以</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">阶级观点</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">进行研究和批判的文章连续出现。因为毛泽东二十年代写过</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">中国社会各阶级的分析</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">，不少作者于是认为</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">坚持阶级分析是研究作品人物的根本出发点</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">，他们用毛泽东的分类法，以及中共五十年代实行土地改革时划分阶级成分的标准，给《红楼梦》人物定成分。结果是大观园里没有一个好人。贾宝玉是花花公子，林黛玉是贵族小姐，晴雯等丫环是欺凌小丫环二级主子。最可笑的是关于刘姥姥的阶级成分，在胡适家乡安徽</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">合肥师范学院</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">的争论中，有人说她是破落地主，有人说她是贫下中农，还有人说她两种成分兼而有之。这种</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">研究方法</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">在</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">文革</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">中更畸形地发展。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　查中国艺术研究院《红楼梦》研究资料室顾平旦主编、刘泊渊、殷小冀整理，北京书目文献出版社出版的《红楼梦》研究论文数据索引（</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1874-1982</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">），</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1966-1972</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年间，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">红学</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">文章在整个大陆的报纸上绝迹了七年；期刊上的情况，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1966</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">、</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1967</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">、</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1968</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">、</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1970</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年，四年空白；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1969</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年和</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1971</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年，各一篇；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1972</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年，七篇；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1969</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年的那一篇登在规格较高的</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">北京师范大学学报</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">上。其它八篇，登在无足轻重的图书馆交流之类的通讯刊物上。万马齐暗，并非仅仅是</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">红学</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">荒芜而已。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1971</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年，美国利用毛泽东的坚决反苏，经多方努力，终于取得改善与中国关系的联络，由于安排尼克松顺利访华的示好需要，美国放弃对中国进入联合国的阻扰。面对飘零在海外、有家但害怕</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">运动</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">而归不得的千万华人，启用诱导文化上的认同。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　首先在</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1972</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family","title":"《红楼梦》的春与秋（续完）","time":1232310271000}